    • parseISOLocalDateTime

      public static LocalDateTime parseISOLocalDateTime(String datetimeStr)
      MySQL has fractional seconds support for TIME, DATETIME, and TIMESTAMP values, with up to microseconds (6 digits) precision. ISO-8601 standard format is with up to nanoseconds (9 digits) precision, which is sufficient for storing MySQL time-related data.
      参数:
      datetimeStr - datetime string
      返回:
      LocalDateTime
